@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_awkcey(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((0.24 / wp.exp(tmp + 0.83)) / wp.cos((v1 + 0.33 + tmp + 0.02)))
    v1 = wp.exp((wp.abs(tmp + 0.50) - wp.cos(v1 + 0.66)))
    v0 = v1
    v2 = (v0 / v0)
    tmp = (wp.exp(0.59) * ((tmp + 0.31 - tmp + 0.13) + 0.73))
    v0 = v0
    data[tid] = v0
